=== Diamonds and hearts

A major-suit is in focus when one of the following applies:

@ it was rebid directly after
_ diamond agreement

@ delayed support was given directly
_ after diamond agreement

@ it was bid on the first round

If diamonds are agreed and then hearts are offered as a possible
trump-suit, then a new suit will reject hearts and reaffirm that
diamonds are trump.

[%autowidth,cols="<",grid="none"]
|===
| After diamond agreement followed by 3H

| a raise of 3H to 4H is an offer to play
| a jump to 4S is kickback for hearts
| 4D indicates: +
  @ no interest in playing in hearts +
  @ nothing more to say
| An unbid suit or 4C reaffirms diamonds as trump
  and shows slam interest +
  > 4H by either player = kickback for diamonds
|===

